\t\n63\t### Corner Radius\n64\t\n65\t| Token | Value |\n66\t|---|---|\n67\t| `sm` | 8dp (chips) |\n68\t| `lg` | 16dp (standard cards) |\n69\t| `pill` | 999dp (pills, avatars) |\n70\t\n71\t---\n72\t\n73\t## 6. Layout Rules\n74\t\n75\t### Scaffold Structure\n76\t\n77\t- `Scaffold` with standard `AppBar` (no SliverAppBar needed)\n78\t- `AppBar`: Title \"Mindfulness\", back button (48dp touch target), no FAB\n79\t- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden on this screen\n80\t- Body: `ListView` with 16dp horizontal padding\n81\t\n82\t### AppBar Behavior\n83\t\n84\t- Background: `lavenderTint` (#F5F3FF)\n85\t- Title: \"Mindfulness\" — `headlineSmall` (SemiBold 20sp), `deepGraphite`\n86\t- Leading: `ArrowBackIOS` icon button with 48dp touch target\n87\t- Center title: `centerTitle: true`\n88\t\n89\t### Body Layout\n90\t\n91\t- `ListView` with two major sections\n92\t- Section vertical spacing: 24dp between major sections\n93\t- Card internal padding: 16dp all sides\n94\t- Card gap: 12dp between cards\n95\t- Bottom safe area: respect home indicator\n96\t\n97\t---\n98\t\n99\t## 7. Sections\n100\t\n101\t### Section 1: Breathing Exercises\n102\t\n103\t**Description:** A card list of breathing exercises with name, duration, and difficulty badge. Tapping a card triggers the `overlay:breathing-exercise` full-screen overlay.\n104\t\n105\t**Widget Type:** `Column` containing section header + `ListView.separated` (vertical)\n106\t\n107\t**Layout:**\n108\t- Section header: \"Breathing Exercises\" (`headlineMedium`, left-aligned)\n109\t- List of `BreathingExerciseCard` widgets\n110\t- Cards separated by 12dp spacing\n111\t\n112\t**Components:**\n113\t\n114\tEach `BreathingExerciseCard` contains:\n115\t- Exercise name (`titleMedium`)\n116\t- Duration text (`bodyMedium`, `stoneGrey`) — e.g., \"2 min\"\n117\t- Difficulty badge chip (`caption`) — \"Beginner\", \"Intermediate\", \"Advanced\"\n118\t- Chevron right icon (`stoneGrey`)\n119\t- Card background: `morningMist` with 16dp radius, soft shadow\n120\t- Entire card is tappable (48dp+ touch target)\n121\t\n122\t**Data Requirements:**\n123\t- Static exercise catalog (no provider for MVP)\n124\t- Exercise fields: `id`, `name`, `durationSeconds`, `difficulty`, `description`\n125\t- Difficulty values: \"Beginner\", \"Intermediate\", \"Advanced\"\n126\t\n127\t**Sample Data:**\n128\t\n129\t```dart\n130\t[\n131\t  { id: \"box-breathing\", name: \"Box Breathing\", duration: 240, difficulty: \"Beginner\", description: \"4-4-4-4 pattern for calm\" },\n132\t  { id: \"deep-breathe\", name: \"Deep Breathing\", duration: 180, difficulty: \"Beginner\", description: \"Simple inhale-exhale relaxation\" },\n133\t  { id: \"4-7-8\", name: \"4-7-8 Technique\", duration: 270, difficulty: \"Intermediate\", description: \"Promotes sleep and reduces anxiety\" },\n134\t  { id: \"energizing\", name: \"Energizing Breath\", duration: 120, difficulty: \"Intermediate\", description: \"Quick energizing breaths\" },\n135\t]\n136\t```\n137\t\n138\t**Interactive Elements:**\n139\t- Tap card → triggers overlay route `overlay:breathing-exercise` with exercise ID parameter\n140\t- Card press feedback: 200ms ease-out scale to 98%\n141\t\n142\t---\n143\t\n144\t### Section 2: Stretching & Self-Care\n145\t\n146\t**Description:** A card list of stretching routines with routine name, trimester suitability, and estimated time. Tapping triggers `overlay:stretching-guide` bottom sheet.\n147\t\n148\t**Widget Type:** `Column` containing section header + `ListView.separated` (vertical)\n149\t\n150\t**Layout:**\n151\t- Section header: \"Stretching & Self-Care\" (`headlineMedium`, left-aligned)\n152\t- List of `StretchingRoutineCard` widgets\n153\t- Cards separated by 12dp spacing\n154\t\n155\t**Components:**\n156\t\n157\tEach `StretchingRoutineCard` contains:\n158\t- Routine name (`titleMedium`)\n159\t- Trimester badge (pill shape, `blushRose` background) — \"All Trimester\", \"1st Tri\", \"2nd Tri\", \"3rd Tri\"\n160\t- Duration text (`bodyMedium`, `stoneGrey`) — e.g., \"10 min\"\n161\t- Chevron right icon (`stoneGrey`)\n162\t- Card background: `morningMist` with 16dp radius, soft shadow\n163\t\n164\t**Data Requirements:**\n165\t- Static routine catalog\n166\t- Routine fields: `id`, `name`, `durationMinutes`, `trimesterSuitability`, `steps`\n167\t\n168\t**Sample Data:**\n169\t\n170\t```dart\n171\t[\n172\t  { id: \"neck-shoulders\", name: \"Neck & Shoulders\", duration: 5, trimester: \"All\", steps: [...] },\n173\t  { id: \"hip-opener\", name: \"Hip Opener\", duration: 10, trimester: \"2nd/3rd\", steps: [...] },\n174\t  { id: \"standing-stretch\", name: \"Standing Stretch\", duration: 8, trimester: \"1st/2nd\", steps: [...] },\n175\t  { id: \"floor-relaxation\", name: \"Floor Relaxation\", duration: 15, trimester: \"All\", steps: [...] },\n176\t]\n177\t```\n178\t\n179\t**Interactive Elements:**\n180\t- Tap card → triggers overlay route `overlay:stretching-guide` with routine ID parameter\n181\t- Card press feedback: 200ms ease-out scale to 98%\n182\t\n183\t---\n184\t\n185\t## 8. Data\n186\t\n187\t### Entities\n188\t\n189\t**BreathingExercise**\n190\t- `id`: String — unique identifier\n191\t- `name`: String — exercise name\n192\t- `durationSeconds`: int — duration in seconds\n193\t- `difficulty`: String — \"Beginner\" | \"Intermediate\" | \"Advanced\"\n194\t- `description`: String — brief description\n195\t\n196\t**StretchingRoutine**\n197\t- `id`: String — unique identifier\n198\t- `name`: String — routine name\n199\t- `durationMinutes`: int — estimated duration in minutes\n200\t- `trimesterSuitability`: String — \"All\" | \"1st/2nd\" | \"2nd/3rd\" | etc.\n201\t- `steps`: List<String> — step-by-step instructions\n202\t\n203\t### State Management\n204\t\n205\t- `SelfCareCheckStateProvider` — tracks mindfulness completion (for Home checklist integration)\n206\t  - On completing a breathing exercise or stretching routine: mark the item complete in `SelfCareCheckState`\n207\t\n208\t### Provider Dependencies (MVP)\n209\t\n210\t- No provider dependency for exercise/routine data (static catalog)\n211\t- `SelfCareCheckState` integration is optional for MVP\n212\t\n213\t---\n214\t\n215\t## 9. Motion\n216\t\n217\t### Entry Animations\n218\t\n219\t- Screen loads with staggered fade-in for sections: 50ms delay between sections\n220\t- Section headers fade in with 200ms `easeOut`\n221\t- Cards cascade with 50ms stagger delay between each card\n222\t\n223\t### Interactive Feedback\n224\t\n225\t- Card tap: 200ms ease-out scale to 98%, then 200ms return to 100%\n226\t- Difficulty/trimester chips: no animation (static badges)\n227\t\n228\t### Overlay Transitions\n229\t\n230\t- Breathing exercise overlay: 300ms slide-up with `Curves.easeInOut` (full-screen)\n231\t- Stretching guide overlay: 250ms slide-up with `Curves.easeOut` (bottom sheet)\n232\t\n233\t---\n234\t\n235\t## 10. Accessibility\n236\t\n237\t### Semantic Labels\n238\t\n239\t| Element | Semantic Label |\n240\t|---|---|\n241\t| AppBar | `'Mindfulness screen, go back'` |\n242\t| Breathing card | `'$name breathing exercise, $duration, $difficulty, tap to start'` |\n243\t| Stretching card | `'$name stretching routine, $duration, tap to view guide'` |\n244\t| Difficulty badge | `'$difficulty level'` |\n245\t| Trimester badge | `'$suitability trimester suitability'` |\n246\t\n247\t### Focus Order\n248\t\n249\t1. AppBar (back button)\n250\t2. Breathing exercises section header\n251\t3. Breathing exercise cards (top to bottom)\n252\t4. Stretching section header\n253\t5. Stretching routine cards (top to bottom)\n254\t\n255\t### Contrast Notes\n256\t\n257\t- All text meets WCAG AA contrast (4.5:1 minimum)\n258\t- `deepGraphite` on `morningMist`: ~12:1\n259\t- `stoneGrey` on `morningMist`: ~4.7:1\n260\t\n261\t### Screen Reader Support\n262\t\n263\t- `ExcludeSemantics` on decorative chevron icons\n264\t- Live region when overlay is triggered: \"Opening $name\"\n265\t\n266\t---\n267\t\n268\t## 11. Anti-Patterns\n269\t\n270\t**Do Not:**\n271\t- Add 