                  });\n454\t                },\n455\t              ),\n456\t            );\n457\t          }),\n458\t        ],\n459\t      ),\n460\t    );\n461\t  }\n462\t\n463\t  List<Map<String, String>> _getSelfCareTips(int week) {\n464\t    const tips = {\n465\t      12: [\n466\t        {\n467\t          'title': 'Stay hydrated',\n468\t          'detail':\n469\t              'Aim for 8-10 glasses of water daily. Staying hydrated helps prevent UTIs and constipation, common during pregnancy.',\n470\t        },\n471\t        {\n472\t          'title': 'Try gentle exercise',\n473\t          'detail':\n474\t              'Walking or prenatal yoga can help with energy levels and prepare your body for labor.',\n475\t        },\n476\t        {\n477\t          'title': 'Schedule your anatomy scan',\n478\t          'detail':\n479\t              'Your 20-week anatomy scan is approaching. This detailed ultrasound checks baby\\'s development and is often covered by insurance.',\n480\t        },\n481\t      ],\n482\t      24: [\n483\t        {\n484\t          'title': 'Practice good posture',\n485\t          'detail':\n486\t              'As your belly grows, focus on standing and sitting with good alignment to reduce back pain.',\n487\t        },\n488\t        {\n489\t          'title': 'Continue staying active',\n490\t          'detail':\n491\t              'Regular low-impact exercise like swimming or walking can help with circulation and energy.',\n492\t        },\n493\t        {\n494\t          'title': 'Start planning the nursery',\n495\t          'detail':\n496\t              'This is a great time to start thinking about nursery themes and gathering essential items.',\n497\t        },\n498\t      ],\n499\t    };\n500\t    return tips[week] ??\n501\t        [\n502\t          {\n503\t            'title': 'Stay hydrated',\n504\t            'detail': 'Drink plenty of water throughout the day.',\n505\t          },\n506\t          {\n507\t            'title': 'Rest when nee